## 2. Extraction Orchestration Data Flow

```mermaid
graph LR
  IN["Client Incoming Request"] --> ING["Ingestion Router"]
  ING --> INT["Intent Validation Engine"]
  INT --> BR["Standard Research Brief"]
  
  BR --> FAST{"Known Source?"}
  FAST -- "Yes" --> SCR["Pre-Built Fast-Track Tool"]
  FAST -- "No" --> SME["SME Deep Mapping"]
  SME --> SGEN["Script Generation Node"]
  SGEN --> SCR

  SCR --> ORCH["Extraction Orchestrator"]
  ORCH --> ADAPT["Browser and API Adapters"]
  ADAPT --> RAW["Raw Unstructured Payload"]
  
  RAW --> TRANS["Target Schema Mapping"]
  TRANS --> QA["Validation & Trust Auditor"]
  QA --> OUT["Secure Extracted Deliverable"]
```

