## 3. Assessment & Discovery Intent Handoff

```mermaid
graph LR
  subgraph P1["Assessment & Interrogation"]
    PAYLOAD["Multimodal Input"]
    ROUTER["Ingestion File Router"]
    INTENT["LLM Intent Extractor"]
    BRIEF["Standardized YAML"]
  end

  subgraph P2["Discovery & Onboarding"]
    CHECK["Catalog Check"]
    CACHE["Pre-Built Evasion Tool"]
    SME["SME Agent Mapping"]
    HITL["Human Review"]
  end

  PAYLOAD --> ROUTER
  ROUTER --> INTENT
  INTENT -- "Missing Required Fields" --> HITL
  INTENT -- "Valid Intent" --> BRIEF

  BRIEF --> CHECK
  CHECK -- "Target Known" --> CACHE
  CHECK -- "Target Unknown" --> SME
  SME -- "Specs Mapped" --> SGEN["Scripting Repo Generation"]
  
  CACHE --> EXEC["Ready for Extraction"]
  SGEN --> EXEC
```

