## 4. Extraction Scaling & Sentinel Pipeline

```mermaid
graph TB
  subgraph SCHED["Phase 1: Scheduling"]
    Q["Job Queue Array"]
    PULL["SLA Triggered Deployment"]
  end

  subgraph EXTR["Phase 3: Extraction Architecture"]
    ROUTE["Adapter Routing"]
    SPAWN["Dynamic Node Spawning"]
    PROXY["Proxy Pool"]
    SCRAPE["Payload Execution Engine"]
  end

  subgraph SENT["Phase 5: Sentinel Monitoring"]
    MON["Failure Detection"]
    RETRY["Exponential Backoff"]
    ALERT["Human Escalation"]
  end

  Q --> PULL
  PULL --> ROUTE
  ROUTE --> SPAWN
  SPAWN --> PROXY
  PROXY --> SCRAPE

  SCRAPE -- "Timeout/IP Block" --> MON
  MON --> RETRY
  RETRY -.-> Q
  MON -- "Hard Failure" --> ALERT
```
